headline: Latest News In Digital Payment - Driving Growth With Real-Time And Recurring Payment Innovations
summary: A recent study by Juniper Research highlights significant growth prospects in the digital payment space, with global Account-to-Account (A2A) payment transaction values projected to rise by 113% over the next five years, reaching $195 trillion by 2030. This growth is being driven by the implementation of real-time payment systems, which are expected to facilitate new payment use cases like instant payroll and real-time bill settlements.
